headline: eBay’s Q3 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: eBay’s third quarter was marked by solid revenue growth but a negative market reaction, as investors focused on margin compression and rising costs. Management attributed revenue gains to strength in focus categories such as trading cards, motor parts, and luxury fashion, as well as the continued rollout of AI-driven seller tools.
